  <h2 id="metrics" class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400">Metrics and tools</h2>
  <h3>Key metrics</h3>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Core Web Vitals (LCP, FCP, CLS, INP)</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Page weight and bundle size</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Error rates and retry success</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Data usage and cache efficiency</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">User engagement and completion rates</li>
  </ul>

